
=== OVD Windows slave server generator ===

I. Software dependencies

	* Python 2.5
		* py2exe
		* pywin32
		* pysvn
	* Java 2.5 jdk
		* ant
	* Mingw gcc
		* make
	* nsis
		* nsis PassDialog plugin (http://nsis.sourceforge.net/PassDialog_plug-in)
	
	* GNU Gettext

	All the software directories have to be defined in the %PATH% 
	variable in order to be able to launch gcc, make, python, 
	java ... from anywhere on the system



II. Download the code and binaries
	mkdir seamlessrdpshell; cd seamlessrdpshell && lftp -e "mirror .; quit" http://devel.ulteo.com/~laurent/OVD/windows/seamlessrdpshell/3.0/; cd ..
	lftp -e "mirror bmp2png; quit" http://devel.ulteo.com/~laurent/OVD/windows/


IV. Compile

	makeServer.py clean all install
